nodes.text: Star Wars Helmet Collection 33 is the thirty-third issue of Star Wars Helmet Collection, published by De Agostini. The issue includes a 1:5 scale replica of Commander Neyo's helmet.

The issue states that Eeth Koth was killed during Order 66. Darth Vader: Dark Lord of the Sith 19, however, later established that he had survived Order 66, by leaving the Jedi Order, before being killed by Darth Vader in a duel.
